; =============================================================================
; ZONE 1: FLAT RUN CORRIDOR
; Long flat surface (x=0 to x=4000) for RUNNING → SLIDING → pop-jump testing
; Ground center: (2000, 520) — surface top at y=500, slab 40px thick
; =============================================================================

