;
; LP1: 150px wide, top y=400, x=1900 — low approach
; LP2: 150px wide, top y=320, x=2100 — gap: 50px horizontal, 80px height diff
; LP3: 150px wide, top y=380, x=2300 — slight drop, 50px gap
; LP4: 150px wide, top y=300, x=2480 — highest, 30px gap, sharpest edge
; StaticBody2D centers at (x, top+8) for each
; =============================================================================

